{"tid":625594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實係咪應該先解決啲南亞狗呢？","createTime":"2018-04-11T14:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T15:38:04.000Z","uid":177406,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"45afab6d7f4e286d1f2161fb4f189cf1626ee1cf","tid":625594,"uid":177406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:55:56.000Z","msg":"今日眼見香港人俾班南亞雜種又搶又打 <br />\n香港係個國際城市<br />\n但係唔代表要接受呢班淨係識搞事，禍港殃民嘅垃圾<br />\n香港人每日都俾呢班狗命一條嘅垃圾威脅住，如果下一個俾人扑濕果個係你，你覺得點？今日元朗先又一單<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180411/mobile/bkn-20180411121326472-0411_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180411%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180411121326472-0411_00822_001.html&d=MXqbSAbZDu%2FemF4bcT8PWcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=c6e18cad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180411/mobile/bkn-20180411121326472-0411_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20160330/mobile/odn-20160330-0330_00176_010.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160330%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20160330-0330_00176_010.html&d=MXqbSAbZDu%2FemF4bcT8PWcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=d918e230\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20160330/mobile/odn-20160330-0330_00176_010.html</a><br />\n<br />\n大家係時候解決吓燃眉之急嘅問題，連登仔女們我相信大家亦都唔想身邊嘅人無端端係街俾人打到訓咗喺度，甚至披血受傷。係時候發揮我哋嘅力量將呢班垃圾排出我哋嘅社會，香港人唔需要你哋班垃圾，我哋有自給自足嘅能力，唔需要你班人渣喺度<br />\n希望連登可以發揮佢嘅能力，一齊捍衛返香港人嘅地位，我哋唔會向你班垃圾雜種低頭，香港人打不死，連登都一樣<br />\n<br />\n最後一句，你班南亞雜種狗祝你地仆街冚家剷死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505e9471ff48a72ee9fe754e10cbc10bfbabd4fc","tid":625594,"uid":61398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:56:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"520c8d4dcccbeeecbbc63645e8082a101a2b4ec5","tid":625594,"uid":177406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"505e9471ff48a72ee9fe754e